thread.title: Open houses for October 17 - 18, 2015

author: KIRSTEN O'BRIEN, SEATTLEPI.COM STAFF
title: Open houses for October 17 - 18, 2015
text:
You tend to get more bang for your buck as you go north of the city, and these homes are no exception. The homes range from $615,000 to $985,000, and all have four or more bedrooms.
The homes are scattered throughout the Cedar Park, Matthews Beach and Meadowbrook neighborhoods, but they're still just a short drive into the city. They also offer one thing that's hard to come by in the city: yard space. Each home has ample room to roam, with lot sizes ranging from 7,200 square feet to almost 10,000 square feet.
